title: Emergency obstetrics
creator_credit: Richard Scott, Pyramid Films and Medi-Cine
brief_description: Shows emergency medical technicians how to assist in emergency childbirth. Demonstrates step-by-step procedures showing two live births and the critical situation of a prolapsed umbilical cord. Narrated by Lynne Littman.
